{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8ebf32ae-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s285t"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"285t"},"text":"§ 285t.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional contribution to special funds; authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id8ebf32af-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s285t/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The United States Governor of the Bank is authorized to contribute on behalf of the United States $180,000,000 to the Asian Development Fund, a special fund of the Bank: ","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided, however","children":[],"tail":", That any commitment to make such contribution shall be made subject to obtaining the necessary appropriations."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id8ebf32b0-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s285t/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In order to pay for the United States contribution to the Asian Development Fund provided for in this section, there are authorized to be appropriated without fiscal year limitation $180,000,000 for payment by the Secretary of the Treasury: ","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided, however","children":[],"tail":", That not more than $14,116,177 may be made available for such contribution for the fiscal year 1982."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8ebf32b1-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/369/s23"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–369, § 23","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/118/tV/s501"},"text":"Pub. 